#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:1
msgid "Quick Start"
msgstr "빠른 시작"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:3
msgid ""
"Get CxFlow up and running in your Odoo 19.0 instance — from installation "
"to your first document in under 10 minutes."
msgstr ""
"Odoo 19.0 인스턴스에서 CxFlow를 설치하고 실행하세요 — 설치부터 첫 번째 "
"문서 작성까지 10분 이내."

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:6
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "사전 요구사항"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:8
msgid "Odoo 19.0 Enterprise with **Project** app installed"
msgstr "**프로젝트** 앱이 설치된 Odoo 19.0 Enterprise"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:9
msgid "Python packages: `markdown-it-py`, `bleach`"
msgstr "Python 패키지: `markdown-it-py`, `bleach`"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:10
msgid "Admin access to install modules"
msgstr "모듈 설치를 위한 관리자 접근 권한"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:12
msgid "Step 1 — Install the Base Module"
msgstr "1단계 — 기본 모듈 설치"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:14
msgid "Install **Linkup CxFlow Docs** (`lu_cxflow_docs`) from the Apps menu."
msgstr "앱 메뉴에서 **Linkup CxFlow Docs** (`lu_cxflow_docs`)를 설치합니다."

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:20
msgid "This creates the **CxFlow** top-level menu with:"
msgstr "이렇게 하면 다음을 포함하는 **CxFlow** 최상위 메뉴가 생성됩니다:"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:22
msgid "**Workspace** — 3-panel document editor"
msgstr "**Workspace** — 3패널 문서 편집기"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:23
msgid "**Documents** — CPS, Deliverables, Reports, Notes"
msgstr "**Documents** — CPS, 산출물, 보고서, 노트"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:24
msgid "**Configuration** — Tags (manager only)"
msgstr "**Configuration** — 태그 (관리자 전용)"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:27
msgid ""
"Install `lu_cxflow_registry` next if you need structured metadata "
"(requirements, processes, test cases). The other modules can be added "
"later as needed."
msgstr ""
"구조화된 메타데이터(요구사항, 프로세스, 테스트 케이스)가 필요하면 "
"`lu_cxflow_registry`를 다음으로 설치하세요. 다른 모듈은 필요에 따라 "
"나중에 추가할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:31
msgid "Step 2 — Create a Project"
msgstr "2단계 — 프로젝트 생성"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:33
msgid ""
"CxFlow documents are scoped to Odoo projects. Create or select an "
"existing project:"
msgstr ""
"CxFlow 문서는 Odoo 프로젝트에 범위가 지정됩니다. 기존 프로젝트를 선택하거나 "
"새로 생성하세요:"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:40
msgid "Step 3 — Open the Workspace"
msgstr "3단계 — Workspace 열기"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:42
msgid ""
"Navigate to **CxFlow → Workspace** and select your project. The workspace"
" provides a 3-panel layout:"
msgstr ""
"**CxFlow → Workspace**로 이동하여 프로젝트를 선택합니다. Workspace는 "
"3패널 레이아웃을 제공합니다:"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:26
msgid "Panel"
msgstr "패널"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:26
msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "용도"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:26
msgid "**Left** — Doc Tree"
msgstr "**왼쪽** — 문서 트리"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:26
msgid "Browse CPS, deliverables, reports, notes in a folder structure"
msgstr "폴더 구조로 CPS, 산출물, 보고서, 노트 탐색"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:26
msgid "**Center** — Editor"
msgstr "**가운데** — 편집기"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:26
msgid "Markdown editor (CodeMirror 6) with live preview"
msgstr "실시간 미리보기를 지원하는 Markdown 편집기 (CodeMirror 6)"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:26
msgid "**Right** — TOC & Meta"
msgstr "**오른쪽** — 목차 및 메타"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:26
msgid "Table of contents, tags, version info, workflow buttons"
msgstr "목차, 태그, 버전 정보, 워크플로우 버튼"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:51
msgid "Step 4 — Create a CPS Document"
msgstr "4단계 — CPS 문서 생성"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:53
msgid ""
"The CPS (Context / Problem / Solution) is the root document for your "
"project. Only one CPS per project is allowed."
msgstr ""
"CPS (Context / Problem / Solution)는 프로젝트의 루트 문서입니다. "
"프로젝트당 하나의 CPS만 허용됩니다."

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:56
msgid "In the Workspace, click **+ New CPS**"
msgstr "Workspace에서 **+ New CPS** 클릭"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:57
msgid "Enter a title (e.g., \"ERP Migration Project\")"
msgstr "제목을 입력 (예: \"ERP Migration Project\")"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:58
msgid "Write your project context in Markdown:"
msgstr "프로젝트 컨텍스트를 Markdown으로 작성:"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:77
msgid "Click **Save**"
msgstr "**Save** 클릭"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:80
msgid ""
"CxFlow stores Markdown as the single source of truth (`md_source`). The "
"HTML preview is computed on-the-fly — you never edit HTML directly."
msgstr ""
"CxFlow는 Markdown을 단일 진실 공급원(`md_source`)으로 저장합니다. "
"HTML 미리보기는 실시간으로 계산되며 — HTML을 직접 편집할 필요가 없습니다."

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:84
msgid "Step 5 — Add Sections"
msgstr "5단계 — 섹션 추가"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:86
msgid "CPS supports hierarchical sections with type annotations:"
msgstr "CPS는 타입 어노테이션을 가진 계층적 섹션을 지원합니다:"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:88
msgid "Click **+ Section** under your CPS"
msgstr "CPS 아래에서 **+ Section** 클릭"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:89
msgid "Set **Section Type** to `context`, `problem`, or `solution`"
msgstr "**Section Type**을 `context`, `problem` 또는 `solution`으로 설정"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:90
msgid "Write the section content in Markdown"
msgstr "Markdown으로 섹션 내용을 작성"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:91
msgid "Drag sections to reorder using the sequence handle"
msgstr "시퀀스 핸들을 사용하여 섹션을 드래그하여 순서 변경"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:93
msgid "Step 6 — Submit for Review"
msgstr "6단계 — 검토 제출"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:95
msgid "When your CPS is ready:"
msgstr "CPS가 준비되면:"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:97
msgid "Click **Submit for Review** in the header"
msgstr "헤더에서 **Submit for Review** 클릭"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:98
msgid "A reviewer (another CxFlow User) reviews and clicks **Request Approval**"
msgstr "리뷰어(다른 CxFlow 사용자)가 검토 후 **Request Approval** 클릭"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:99
msgid "A CxFlow Manager clicks **Approve**"
msgstr "CxFlow Manager가 **Approve** 클릭"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:102
msgid ""
"The full workflow is: **Draft → Review → Approval → Approved**. Reports "
"use a simpler 2-state flow (Draft → Approved), and Notes use Draft → "
"Archived."
msgstr ""
"전체 워크플로우는: **Draft → Review → Approval → Approved**입니다. "
"보고서는 더 단순한 2단계 흐름(Draft → Approved)을 사용하고, "
"노트는 Draft → Archived를 사용합니다."

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:107
msgid "What's Next?"
msgstr "다음 단계"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:101
msgid "Goal"
msgstr "목표"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:101
msgid "Chapter"
msgstr "챕터"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:101
msgid "Learn all document types and versioning"
msgstr "모든 문서 유형과 버전 관리 학습"

#: ../../cxflow/quickstart.md:101
#, python-brace-format
msgid "{doc}`document-management`"
msgstr "{doc}`document-management`"

